text: Samson and Delilah is a 1922 Austrian historical adventure movie directed by Alexander Korda and stars María Corda, Franz Herterich, Ernst Arndt, Alfredo Boccolini, Paul Lukas. It was distributed by Rosenhügel Film Studios. ==Other websites== * * Category:1922 adventure movies Category:Austrian adventure movies Category:Austrian silent movies Category:Movies directed by Alexander Korda
